<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I have read Terry&apos;s books in the haphazard fashion in which I found them at second hand shops, libraries and stores. It had no effect on my enjoyment.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I have read Terry's books in the haphazard fashion in which I found them at second hand shops, libraries and stores. It had no effect on my enjoyment. I now own them all. Read whatever you can get!<br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
